Package: IsoformUniverse
Title: An Umbrella Package for Isoform Analysis Tools
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Elena", "Iri", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "elena@example.com")
Description: An umbrella package that installs, updates, and loads a curated
    set of R packages for isoform-level analysis. Inspired by how the
    'tidyverse' package manages its ecosystem, 'IsoformUniverse' manages
    packages hosted on Bioconductor and GitHub. Running
    library(IsoformUniverse) attaches all member packages and prints a
    startup message. Convenience functions allow you to install or update
    all member packages with a single call.
